  "sketchCode": "// Lesson 2 — Read a Button\n// When the button is pressed, the LED turns on.\n\nvoid setup() {\n  pinMode(2, INPUT_PULLUP);\n  pinMode(13, OUTPUT);\n}\n\nvoid loop() {\n  if (digitalRead(2) == LOW) {\n    digitalWrite(13, HIGH);\n  } else {\n    digitalWrite(13, LOW);\n  }\n}\n",
